{"tid":757572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"根據歐盟外交部主席，中國高官及學者大多被Trump嘅戰略「震懾」","createTime":"2018-07-27T03:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T20:37:54.000Z","uid":131691,"like":80,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"b7ef049ec9206ff933bc85bfa3eaaa7a66497e30","tid":757572,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T03:19:13.000Z","msg":"Mark Leonard引述，訪華嘅時候接觸過多個中國高官及學者，都同佢講佢哋被Trump嘅戰略同策略「震懾」，因為Trump係40年來第一個人能夠同時間打壓中國三方面：貿易，軍事，仲有意識形態（ideology）。<br />\n<br />\nLeonard繼續引述，好多中國高官、學者都認為Trump嘅言行係「創意性破壞」，務求摧毀現有對美國不利嘅系統，從而改寫世界政治。雖然中國官方取態強硬，但係好多中國人都認為同美國硬碰係冇好下場，應該學識配合美國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.breitbart.com/big-government/2018/07/26/report-chinese-are-awed-by-trumps-skill-as-a-strategist-and-tactician/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.breitbart.com%2Fbig-government%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2Freport-chinese-are-awed-by-trumps-skill-as-a-strategist-and-tactician%2F&d=rPk%2BqPz8NcK6ymllK2Cm5U%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=725f268f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.breitbart.com/big-government/2018/07/26/report-chinese-are-awed-by-trumps-skill-as-a-strategist-and-tactician/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/f83b20e4-8e67-11e8-9609-3d3b945e78cf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Ff83b20e4-8e67-11e8-9609-3d3b945e78cf&d=rPk%2BqPz8NcK6ymllK2Cm5U%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=2a56da25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ft.com/content/f83b20e4-8e67-11e8-9609-3d3b945e78cf</a>"},{"pid":"aa8748a94f8f3bf81a2a93ba8b907cb83625667e","tid":757572,"uid":131691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T03:22:42.000Z","msg":"中國背後其實有好多好驚驚嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c15be2a368da8b21d6606ae38705bf8d2eb3f3a","tid":757572,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T03:24:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" cla